reviewText: This is a very basic DVD. You can find any of this on youtube for free. Duke, Mike Kryzewski, and $45.00. I would have expected much better.

This DVD of Coach Mike Krzyzewski is great, especially for the Middle & High School students in the basketball leagues, especially develope the young basketball players & coaches more on game's stragedies.  Please enjoy this product & I sure did, thank you. Win / lose, good / bad calls, it is all about having some fun in life.
